    "description": "一款带有创新元素的街机清版射击游戏！ 在这款游戏中，你需要打爆越来越密集的气球大军，解锁具有独特技能的角色，并踏上跨越多个世界的冒险之旅！ 在游戏过程中完成各种挑战，解锁提供独特障碍的各个关卡。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279450/extras/90c8376d723c536178fcc4f08d71b1a1.avif?t=1726882458\" width=600 height=105 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279450/extras/3f195b67217756a220842a8d81472c81.poster.avif?t=1726882458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279450/extras/3f195b67217756a220842a8d81472c81.webm?t=1726882458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279450/extras/3f195b67217756a220842a8d81472c81.mp4?t=1726882458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在各个激动人心的地点完成一系列有趣的挑战！ 使用不同的角色重复游玩以精通他们，并争取获得铜牌、银牌和金牌！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279450/extras/b5c928611dcd896cd441de1e6686daee.avif?t=1726882458\" width=600 height=105 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279450/extras/ea3c07f5c1abd5d6a18611068b21cb5f.poster.avif?t=1726882458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279450/extras/ea3c07f5c1abd5d6a18611068b21cb5f.webm?t=1726882458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279450/extras/ea3c07f5c1abd5d6a18611068b21cb5f.mp4?t=1726882458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>穿梭于各个世界，迎战敌人，拯救朋友，然后用它们来进行游戏！ 你解锁的每个新角色都拥有特殊能力，提供多样化的游戏风格。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279450/extras/f9ab5df179276ab8c5cdda5141ffa10b.avif?t=1726882458\" width=600 height=105 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279450/extras/e97a7dce4822735d18d7919fa074ca1a.poster.avif?t=1726882458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279450/extras/e97a7dce4822735d18d7919fa074ca1a.webm?t=1726882458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279450/extras/e97a7dce4822735d18d7919fa074ca1a.mp4?t=1726882458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在写着你名字（冲你而来）的无尽气球大军中努力坚持到最后。<br>尽可能在不断追逐你的无尽气球大军中不断前进！ 每个关卡都有新的挑战和不同的威胁。 可以通过排行榜跟踪你的进度。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279450/extras/54038f19b78a807ac0b99369b71ba976.avif?t=1726882458\" width=600 height=105 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279450/extras/7d82c1638c521a7ca32b17a09372eb7d.poster.avif?t=1726882458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279450/extras/7d82c1638c521a7ca32b17a09372eb7d.webm?t=1726882458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279450/extras/7d82c1638c521a7ca32b17a09372eb7d.mp4?t=1726882458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>对抗这场气球入侵背后的反派！ 每个 Boss 都为玩家提供了独特的挑战。 从打爆女王气球到吓跑吞噬怪！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >其他特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 具有独特技能的可解锁角色<br></li><li> 难度逐渐增加的众多关卡<br></li><li> 大量成就等你解锁<br></li><li> 多样的配件选择<br></li><li> 完整的手柄支持<br></li><li> 支持单人或多人合作游戏<br></li><li> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li></li></ul>连续 Boss 战！！！</li></ul>",
